{"tid":1507361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"討論佢地會用咩招數令大家阻唔到機場","createTime":"2019-08-26T06:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T22:58:44.000Z","uid":41477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"033ff9f06e4f7823f88ace2fe1db3b74c6fb853a","tid":1507361,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:17:48.000Z","msg":"我覺得有機會係咁：<br />\n機鐵由香港站做檢查，全世界都要係個度上，有機票passport先可以上車，直去機場<br />\n博覽館到機場暫停。<br />\n車路由青衣，東涌開始檢查，無證明既唔俾入機場<br />\n普通人唯一方法係坐巴士入，一落巴士即檢查，無證明係工作人員/登機既即趕或即拉。<br />\n行入去就更加唔駛諗，係入機場島設大批防暴已經搞掂"},{"pid":"398e8604bdef656b64127c75b9a08e77200cee83","tid":1507361,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:18:14.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=411cc939\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"1906d20bae559663bfe8c6adaeb37746b3df9921","tid":1507361,"uid":119729,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:19:25.000Z","msg":"如果佢做得出呢D, 我地塞機場個行動當贏左架喇<br />\n到時遊客只會鬧政府"},{"pid":"0c322da8437220f236a32cd6a1afb73ddc36ee99","tid":1507361,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:23:20.000Z","msg":"機鐵由香港站做檢查,到時大條道理返工遲到"},{"pid":"2eb279147b1328cf49fc73f7ed4e53892b030982","tid":1507361,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:23:32.000Z","msg":"機管局831向法庭申請禁制令<br />\n禁止機場9月1至10月5 所有集會示威<br />\n同時要有機票先可進入機場<br />\n<br />\n如果想搞和你塞<br />\n政府免費機鐵俾旅客, 機鐵站設特別通道<br />\n或者搞旅遊巴接送<br />\n<br />\n政府：太易玩鳥"},{"pid":"71bb7addbab6dc8a82b2293795cd49780408f1a2","tid":1507361,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite